Package: energystar.gov
Title: ENERGY STAR Certified Products API Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the ENERGY STAR certified products
    database on data.energystar.gov (Socrata SODA API). Covers 70+ product
    categories including computers, displays, appliances, HVAC, lighting,
    and EV chargers. Discovery via catalog search and direct data access
    with SoQL filtering.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
